[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0417","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0417.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0232","title":"NCSA HTTPD 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 1.5c 版本在处理 HTTP 请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送超长或特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致远程代码执行或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.5c 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，且无需认证即可利用。由于该软件已停止维护，建议用户迁移至 Apache httpd 等受支持的 Web 服务器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0232"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.893","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 NCSA HTTPd 1.5c，无官方补丁。建议立即迁移至活跃维护的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 2.4.x 或 Nginx）。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上限制对 80/TCP 端口的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0232","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0232.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0232","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0232.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83083/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0417.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0416","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0416.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0231","title":"IP-Switch IMail 和 Seattle Labs Slmail 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IP-Switch IMail 与 Seattle Labs Slmail 2.6 邮件服务软件中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 SMTP 服务发送超长 VRFY 命令参数触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致服务拒绝服务，在特定条件下可进一步实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响上述邮件系统的 SMTP 组件，利用无需认证，攻击门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0231"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.770","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 SLMail 2.6 及更早版本的 VRFY 命令处理中，超长参数导致栈缓冲区溢出。厂商后续版本已修复此问题，建议尽快升级至 SLMail 3.0 及以上版本，或迁移至 Ipswitch IMail 最新版本。若无法立即升级，应在 SMTP 代理或 IPS 设备上限制 VRFY 命令参数长度不超过 256 字节，并禁用 VRFY/EXPN 命令以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0231","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0231","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0231.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5r6m-8793-wrhh/GHSA-5r6m-8793-wrhh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e1310