rse/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0230.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0415.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0414","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0414.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0228","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RPC Locator 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 RPC Locator 服务（rpcss.exe）存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求，导致 RPC 定位服务进程崩溃或停止响应，影响系统正常功能。该漏洞无需身份认证即可触发，攻击复杂度低，危害等级中等。Microsoft 官方已发布安全更新解决此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0228"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.410","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对此漏洞发布的热修复补丁 KB Q162567，该补丁解决了 rpcss.exe 在处理特定 RPC 请求时的拒绝服务问题。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已于 2004 年终止支持且不再接收安全更新，建议升级至仍在支持周期内的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）。临时缓解措施：在不需要 RPC Locator 服务的环境中，通过 services.msc 将 Remote Procedure Call (RPC) Locator 服务启动类型设为\"禁用\"，或在防火墙上限制对该服务端口 (TCP 135) 的不必要访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ162567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0228","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0228.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7hpc-4h5x-v8cw/GHSA-7hpc-4h5x-v8cw.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0228.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0414.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0413","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0413.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0227","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 LSA/LSARPC 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的本地安全认证子系统服务（LSASS.EXE）在处理 LSA/LSARPC 请求时存在访问冲突漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求，触发 LSASS.EXE 进程崩溃，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，但无法实现远程代码执行或提权。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0227"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.290","remediation":"建议升级至受支持版本的 Windows（Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2019/2022 等），Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持且不再发布安全更新。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上阻止 TCP 135 (RPC) 和 139 (NetBIOS) 端口的入站连接，限制 LSARPC 接口的远程访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ154087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0227","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0227.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80917/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--87f50d43-aca9-4ba6-b704-6b3b4ebdaad2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d6641cf4b3c3f049679d3cd7a1e7c74ad9ced77c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0413.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0411","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0411.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0225","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SMB 登录请求长度错误拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 SMB 登录验证服务在处理畸形登录请求时存在逻辑缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送实际数据大小与指定大小不符的特制 SMB 登录请求包，导致目标系统 LSASS 进程崩溃或系统蓝屏，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 所有版本，攻击条件简单，无需用户交互。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0225"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.050","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 以修复 SMB 登录请求中数据大小校验缺失导致的拒绝服务漏洞。同时建议在网络防火墙层面阻断来自不可信网络的 SMB 端口（TCP 139/445）入站流量。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持超过 20 年，长期缓解措施应迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.microsoft.com/technet/support/kb.asp?ID=180963","http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/25_windows_nt_dos_adv.asp","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0225.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0225","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/b253eed42806cfea7592c1858184a214ab406ebe/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0225.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000260.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d6641cf4b3c3f049679d3cd7a1e7c74ad9ced77c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0411.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0410","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0410.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0220","title":"IRC Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IRC 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 IRC 服务器发送特制数据包，导致服务器进程崩溃，使其无法为正常用户提供聊天服务。该漏洞影响多种 IRC 服务器软件，攻击者仅需具备网络访问能力即可触发，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0220"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.423","remediation":"升级 ircd 至 2.10.3 及以上版本，该版本已修复因畸形数据包导致的服务器崩溃问题。对于无法升级的旧系统，可在 IRC 服务前端部署 TCP 代理或应用层防火墙，过滤异常连接请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0220","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0220.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0220","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rhw-5hch-3fh6/GHSA-9rhw-5hch-3fh6.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80885/info.html","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0220.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0410.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0409","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0409.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0722","title":"Cobalt RaQ2 默认配置远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Cobalt RaQ2 服务器默认配置存在安全缺陷，未对远程用户的软件包安装权限进行有效限制。攻击者无需身份认证即可通过默认开放的远程管理接口向服务器安装任意软件包，进而获得服务器的完全控制权。该漏洞严重影响所有采用默认配置的 Cobalt RaQ2 设备，可导致数据泄露、服务中断等严重后果。建议管理员立即修改默认配置并限制远程访问权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0722"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.193","remediation":"立即登录 Cobalt RaQ2 管理控制台，在 \"System Administration > Remote Package Installation\" 中取消勾选 \"Allow remote installation\"，然后应用保存。在防火墙层面，限制对 TCP 81 端口（管理界面）的访问来源仅为受信任的管理 IP 段。由于该产品已停止维护，建议将服务迁移至受支持的 Linux 发行版（如 CentOS/RHEL 替代方案）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/558"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0409.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0408","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0721","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0/2000 Local Security Authority Subsystem LSA Request 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 的本地安全机构子系统（LSA）存在输入验证漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形 LSA 请求，导致 LSA 服务崩溃，造成系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 等版本，无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级高。Microsoft 官方已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0721"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.073","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-021 提供的安全更新补丁，或升级至 Windows 2000 Service Pack 1 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在防火墙层面过滤发往 LSA 服务的异常 TCP/UDP 流量作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231457","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-049.shtml","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-020"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0407","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0407.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0219","title":"Cat Soft Serv-U FTP Server 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Cat Soft Serv-U FTP Server 2.5 存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞。已认证的远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务发送超长的 CWD（切换目录）或 LS（列出文件）命令触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Serv-U FTP Server 2.5 版本，攻击者只需拥有有效账号即可利用，无需其他特殊权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0219"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.290","remediation":"升级至 Serv-U 2.5a 或更高版本可修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞。当前最新版为 SolarWinds Serv-U 15.x，建议立即升级并开启自动更新。如无法升级，可在防火墙限制 FTP 端口（21/TCP）仅对可信来源开放，并禁用匿名用户写权限作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92574916930144&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92582581330282&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/269","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/205","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19218","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0219.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0219","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0219.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0219.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5495-52g6-8q95/GHSA-5495-52g6-8q95.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/F/ftp_servu_dos.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0219.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/ftp_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0407.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0406","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0710","title":"Squid cachemgr.cgi 未授权连接漏洞","description":"Squid 代理服务器在安装时将 cachemgr.cgi 管理脚本放置在公开 Web 目录下，导致远程攻击者无需认证即可直接访问该脚本，并利用其作为中转代理连接到任意内部或外部系统，造成信息泄露与未授权资源访问。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 5.2/6.0 及包含 Squid 2.2 之前版本的其他发行版，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0710"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.680","remediation":"立即从 Apache CGI 目录（如 /var/www/cgi-bin/）中移除 cachemgr.cgi 脚本，或通过 Apache 配置添加访问控制（Order deny,allow; Deny from all）仅允许受信 IP 访问。同时安装 Red Hat RHSA-1999-025 或 Debian DSA-576 提供的 Squid 安全更新包，升级至修复版本。如无法立即打补丁，可在 cachemgr.cgi 所在目录创建 .htaccess 文件添加 HTTP 基本认证作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://fedoranews.org/updates/FEDORA--.shtml","http://www.debian.org/security/2004/dsa-576","http://www.redhat.com/archives/fedora-announce-list/2005-May/msg00025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-1999-025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2005-489.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/archives/rh52-errata-general.html#squid","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2059","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2385","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20465"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0405","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0405.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0218","title":"Livingston Portmaster 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Livingston Portmaster 远程访问服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标设备发送一系列特制命令，导致设备异常重启，造成正常服务中断。该漏洞影响 Livingston 多款 Portmaster 型号，攻击者只需网络可达即可触发，利用难度较低。厂商已发布修复固件，建议升级至最新版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0218"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.173","remediation":"立即升级至 Livingston/Lucent 发布的最新固件版本（若设备尚在运行且厂商已停止支持，则无官方补丁可用）。作为临时缓解措施，在边界防火墙或路由器 ACL 中限制对 Portmaster 管理端口（Telnet 23/SSH/SNMP）的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理 IP 段连接；同时禁用不必要的远程管理协议（如 Telnet），改用带外管理方式，并严格限制未授权的网络命令输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0218","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0218.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0218","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0218.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0218.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0218.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/713.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0218.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0405.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0403","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0403.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0216","title":"Linux Kernel inetd SYN/RST Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 版本的 inetd 超级服务守护进程存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标主机发送特制的 SYN 和 RST 数据包，导致 inetd 服务异常终止或资源耗尽，无法正常响应合法连接请求。该漏洞影响运行 inetd 服务的 Linux 系统，攻击者无需认证即可实施攻击，且无需目标系统上存在特定监听服务。利用方式简单，通过发送大量伪造的 TCP SYN/RST 包即可触发，属于典型的网络层拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0216"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.917","remediation":"建议将 legacy inetd 替换为 xinetd，并在配置中设置 per_source = 5、cps = 25 30、max_load = 3 以限制并发连接和速率。或者迁移至 systemd socket 激活机制，利用内核 SYN cookies（sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1）和 iptables/nftables 限制入站 SYN 包速率（如 iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn -m limit --limit 10/s -j ACCEPT）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0216","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0216","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0216.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g7qq-2qq9-j34m/GHSA-g7qq-2qq9-j34m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2bbcf0ff-3ba8-4c91-aea6-e3d5fdb0e178.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/linux.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0403.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0402","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0402.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0215","title":"SGI IRIX 和 OpenLinux routed 守护进程文件追加漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 3/4/5/6 及 OpenLinux 1.0/1.1 系统中运行的 routed 路由守护进程存在文件追加写入漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标系统的 routed 服务发送特制的 traceon 路由跟踪数据包，将任意数据追加到系统文件末尾，包括 /etc/passwd 等关键文件，进而实现权限提升或系统控制。该漏洞利用无需认证，远程即可触发，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0215"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-10-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.790","remediation":"建议禁用 routed 服务并改用静态路由或 gated 替代。如确需运行，升级到 IRIX 6.5.2+ 或 OpenLinux 1.1.2+ 版本，并在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 routed 条目后重启 inetd 服务以立即消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-012.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20805","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0215","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0215.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-45w3-m25h-r87g/GHSA-45w3-m25h-r87g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--580f5a91-46c0-44d8-8dec-8f18301e9dd8.json","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0402.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0401","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0401.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0214","title":"Sun SunOS 4.1 ICMP Unreachable 报文拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Microsystems SunOS 4.1/4.1.1/4.1.2 操作系统存在 ICMP 不可达数据包处理缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标主机发送伪造的 ICMP Unreachable 数据包，导致目标系统内核错误地关闭受影响 TCP 连接，造成合法服务中断。该漏洞影响所有运行上述版本 SunOS 的系统，攻击门槛低、危害较大。厂商已发布相应补丁修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0214"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1992-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.663","remediation":"升级 SunOS 至 4.1.3 或更高版本，该版本修复了 ICMP Unreachable 报文处理逻辑。在网络边界防火墙配置规则，过滤外部传入的伪造 ICMP 不可达数据包。如系统仍在使用且无法升级，可考虑迁移至受支持的 Solaris 版本。禁用不必要的 ICMP 响应功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0214"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0401.toml"}]